He's still not moving.

826
00:56:35,938 --> 00:56:37,147
He's still not moving.

827
00:56:38,106 --> 00:56:39,441
He's still not moving.

828
00:57:09,221 --> 00:57:12,724
<i>The next morning, Mitch-Mitch was arrested
for Desertion and Desecration,</i>

829
00:57:12,891 --> 00:57:14,393
<i>and the</i> Sans Blague<i> became headquarters...</i>

830
00:57:14,560 --> 00:57:16,895
<i>for the Movement of Young Idealists
