00:58:19,750 --> 00:58:21,001
<i>September.</i>

840
00:58:21,168 --> 00:58:23,837
Sans Blague<i> coffee license
revoked by official decree.</i>

841
00:58:25,881 --> 00:58:27,090
<i>October.</i>

842
00:58:27,257 --> 00:58:29,218
<i>Propaganda Committee erects
pirate radio tower...</i>

843
00:58:29,384 --> 00:58:31,178
<i>on Physics Department rooftop.</i>

844
00:58:32,596 --> 00:58:33,722
<i>November.</i>

845
00:58:33,889 --> 00:58:36,808
<i>Meal plan blockade
